             depos'd that about 2 in the Morning (the Moon shining) as himself with a Flail, the Deceased with a Hedge Stake, and 
               <persName id="t17220907-31-person171">
                  John 
                  Screen 
               <interp inst="t17220907-31-person171" type="surname" value="Screen"></interp>
