            , since absented, were walking 160 Yards from <placeName id="t17220907-31-crimeloc162">Twittenham Warren</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17220907-31-crimeloc162" type="placeName" value="Twittenham Warren"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17220907-31-crimeloc162" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17220907-31-off161 t17220907-31-crimeloc162"></join>, the prisoner came up with a Quarter Staff, and knock'd the Deceased down, whereupon the other two run away, and left the Deceased; That they had three Dogs with them. Mr. Perkins, the Surgeon, depos'd, that about One in the Morning the prisoner call'd him up to take care of the Deceas'd; but when he came be found him dead. That he opened the Head, and saw the Skull broke, which was the cause of his death. Not far from the prisoner, he found a Cony newly kill'd. 
               <persName id="t17220907-31-person172">
                  Mary 
                  Steward 
               <interp inst="t17220907-31-person172" type="surname" value="Steward"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17220907-31-person172" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17220907-31-person172" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , the prisoner's Witness, depos'd, that she saw 3 Men advance toward the prisoner, who askt then what they were at. That she ran back to call assistance, and before she got in, heard the prisoner cry. Mr. Turner, come help me. She heard the Dogs bark, and Sticks rattle. Mr. Turner deposed, on Mary's crying out, he hastended to the prisoner; that the Deceased was lying by him. They asked him why he came there, he said in was the first time, and begged their pardon. Mrs. Cunningham confirmed the same. 
               <persName id="t17220907-31-person173">
                  John 
                  Chun 
               <interp inst="t17220907-31-person173" type="surname" value="Chun"></interp>
